description.narrative: This integrated, multi-sectoral program will be technically complementary to another new USAID/Yemen project, the Responsive Governance Project (RGP). This project is intended to mitigate the drivers of instability in some of Yemens most difficult areas through the facilitation and implementation of quality government service delivery, job creation, responsive local governance, and active civic participation.
